{"tid":882530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[又贏]【負債纍纍】海航擬首次出售核心航空業務","createTime":"2018-10-30T07:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T07:58:23.000Z","uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf0ed8179004afeeaf9d270b25c1108ab375391","tid":882530,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:49:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=325464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D325464&d=nXiuCq19S5s3zIm%2Bc6BWl9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=74e278e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D325464&h=49251ae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=325464</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】有報道指，海航集團計劃向中國東方航空等，出售祥鵬航空股權。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《金融時報》報道，由於海航債務高達780億美元，折合5420億元人民幣，影響核心營運。海航計劃向競爭對手之一的東航集團，出售地區航空公司祥鵬航空60%股權，而其餘40%股權將向雲南國資委出售。如果成事將會是海航首次出售核心航空業務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賣左出去養過第二間, 又贏"},{"pid":"9e4908dab82653ecfa0f8d41fc435f6d896e027e","tid":882530,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"海航核心業務<br />\n唔係航空業務<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83233a9e93019e24c304b5d708193f441f4cd6e","tid":882530,"uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e4908dab82653ecfa0f8d41fc435f6d896e027e","tid":882530,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"海航核心業務<br />\n唔係航空業務<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"大陸燒烤叫羊肉夠比老鼠肉啦<br />\n呢個係國家既暗號, 唔同文化唔明嫁啦<br />\n我叫緊燒賣, 其實係要蝦餃呀"},{"pid":"9015c7a3e44b379bd05b56bab22d16bd61b6a890","tid":882530,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a83233a9e93019e24c304b5d708193f441f4cd6e","tid":882530,"uid":574